<node CREATED="1518883501447" ID="ID_658907720" MODIFIED="1518883501931" TEXT="Almost all Machine Learning algorithms use Matrix algebra in one way or another. This is a broad subject, too large to be included here in it&#x2019;s full length. Here&#x2019;s a start: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_(mathematics)">
