<node CREATED="1518883681172" ID="ID_368043493" MODIFIED="1518883681863" TEXT="Eigenvectors and Eigenvalues">
<node CREATED="1518883694451" ID="ID_1313616741" MODIFIED="1518883696303" TEXT="In linear algebra, an eigenvector or characteristic vector of a linear transformation T from a vector space V over a field F into itself is a non-zero vector that does not change its direction when that linear transformation is applied to it.">
